For this challenge you need to create a simple SELECT statement. Your task is to calculate the MIN, MEDIAN and MAX scores of the students from the results table.

Tables and relationship below:

Student Table:
Id
Name

Result:
Id
Student_id
Score

Resultant table:
min
median
max

To calculate median in Postgresql:
Link: https://www.compose.com/articles/metrics-maven-meet-in-the-middle-median-in-postgresql/

